    ByStateCommandHandlerImpl

    public class CommandHandlerImpl<Command,Event,State>
extends CommandHandler<Command,Event,State>
implements ReplicatedEntity.CommandHandler<Command,Event,State>
    Command handlers and optional functions for other signals, e.g. Termination messages if watch is used. CommandHandlerImpl is an immutable class.
